traffic.signal

Class SignalFace

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • traffic.signal.SignalFace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Observer

    public class SignalFace
extends Observable
implements Observer, Serializable
    Class to represent a set of lights under the control of a traffic stream which in turn is under the control of a phase. Extends Observable so that monitor style interfaces capable of responding to changes in the state of a signal face can be built readily. Each signal face contains three (green, red and yellow) lights of identical shape.
    See Also:
    Light, ArrowLight, Serialized Form
